r service, and the controller. I also need to expand the CSV with more training data so the model has something reasonable to work with.\n\nFor the ML.NET multiclass classification pipeline, I'll featurize the text columns (Subject and Description) and convert Priority to a numeric label...\n\nSetting up the trainer and mapping the label back to key.","outputTokens":656,"requestId":"AC09:310F9A:B0E902:DB1519:6A012A5D"},"id":"fa40c86a-1fd2-4702-9f3a-3607ea46ce9a","timestamp":"2026-05-11T01:01:35.690Z","parentId":"b057b417-77af-41e0-8806-d86df9eaeb2a"}
